@gateway = http://localhost:5000

### Gateway routes
GET {{gateway}}/routes

### Gateway health
GET {{gateway}}/health

### Security API through gateway
GET {{gateway}}/security/api/users

### Login through gateway
POST {{gateway}}/security/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "demo",
  "password": "demo"
}

### Profile API through gateway
GET {{gateway}}/profile/api/profiles

### Game API through gateway
POST {{gateway}}/game/api/games/game-001/sessions

### Store API through gateway
POST {{gateway}}/store/api/orders/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "usr-001",
  "productId": "product-001",
  "total": 9.99
}

### Teams API through gateway
POST {{gateway}}/teams/api/teams/team-001/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "usr-003",
  "role": "Member"
}
